      "rationale": "Nonlinear solver residuals monitored at each load step; force residual norm <1e-4 and displacement residual norm <1e-5 at convergence for all load cases. Iterative solver (PCG) tolerance 1e-8. Gradation 1 satisfied for a quasi-static structural analysis of this complexity."
