      "rationale": "Continuum elastoplastic material model (bilinear isotropic hardening) used for titanium alloy; validated against uniaxial coupon data (R²=0.997). Frictional contact (mu=0.2) at screw-rod and rod-block interfaces based on published tribological data for Ti-6Al-4V on UHMWPE. Model form appropriate for quasi-static large-displacement bending regime. Gradation 2 achieved."
