      "rationale": "All material properties derived from lot-specific coupon testing (N=8 Ti-6Al-4V coupons per lot; E=110±6 GPa, Sy=880±22 MPa). Geometric inputs from CMM measurements of production screws (N=5 per dimension). Input uncertainty distributions propagated via Monte Carlo (500 samples). Confidence approximately 50% due to moderate N; wide bounds honestly reported and propagated into validation uncertainty. Gradation 2 achieved because distributions are measured and propagated, even if confidence is moderate."
