      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. All samples drawn from production lots; dimensional inspection confirms conformance to design drawings. Sample size is acknowledged as modest (CV 8–11% across QoIs); this contributes to the ~50% confidence level, which is documented honestly. N=11 satisfies Gradation 2 for a Medium model-risk COU per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 guidance."
    },
    {
