      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/test-conditions-level2-standard-protocol",
      "rationale": "Testing performed per ASTM F1717-21 standard protocol at ambient temperature (23±2°C) and humidity (50±10% RH). Single test condition (standard F1717 offset load, 5 mm/min displacement rate) acknowledged as a limitation; only one loading rate and temperature condition evaluated. This limitation is documented honestly and accepted as a known constraint of the F1717 standard. The single standardized condition is nonetheless a well-characterized, reproducible protocol and satisfies Gradation 2 for this COU."
    },
    {
