      "rationale": "FEA model inputs (geometry, material properties, boundary conditions) directly matched to as-tested specimen measurements and test fixture dimensions. Fixture compliance measured and incorporated as a spring boundary condition (k_fixture=8200 N/mm). Dimensional equivalency confirmed for all 11 specimens via CMM data. Gradation 2 achieved."
