      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed using pre-specified acceptance bounds: relative QoI error <10% and E/uval<1.96. Results: stiffness error 2.6% (E/uval=0.43), yield force error 2.3% (E/uval=0.20), force at 40 mm error 1.6% (E/uval=0.12). All three QoIs satisfy both criteria. Wide uncertainty bounds (confidence ~50%) are propagated into uval, making E/uval a conservative metric. Gradation 2 achieved."
